  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0001",
          "zh": "老子者，楚苦縣厲鄉曲仁里人也，姓李氏，名耳，字耼，周守藏室之史也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0002",
          "zh": "孔子適周，將問禮於老子。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0003",
          "zh": "老子曰：「子所言者，其人與骨皆已朽矣，獨其言在耳。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0004",
          "zh": "且君子得其時則駕，不得其時則蓬累而行。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0005",
          "zh": "吾聞之，良賈深藏若虛，君子盛德容貌若愚。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0006",
          "zh": "去子之驕氣與多欲，態色與淫志，是皆無益於子之身。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0007",
          "zh": "吾所以告子，若是而已。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0008",
          "zh": "孔子去，謂弟子曰：「鳥，吾知其能飛；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0009",
          "zh": "魚，吾知其能游；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0010",
          "zh": "獸，吾知其能走。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0011",
          "zh": "走者可以為罔，游者可以為綸，飛者可以為矰。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0012",
          "zh": "至於龍，吾不能知其乘風雲而上天。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0013",
          "zh": "吾今日見老子，其猶龍邪！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0015",
          "zh": "老子修道德，其學以自隱無名為務。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0016",
          "zh": "居周久之，見周之衰，乃遂去。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0017",
          "zh": "至關，關令尹喜曰：「子將隱矣，彊為我著書。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0018",
          "zh": "於是老子乃著書上下篇，言道德之意五千餘言而去，莫知其所終。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0019",
          "zh": "或曰：老萊子亦楚人也，著書十五篇，言道家之用，與孔子同時云。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0020",
          "zh": "蓋老子百有六十餘歲，或言二百餘歲，以其修道而養壽也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0021",
          "zh": "自孔子死之後百二十九年，而史記周太史儋見秦獻公曰：「始秦與周合，合五百歲而離，離七十歲而霸王者出焉。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0022",
          "zh": "或曰儋即老子，或曰非也，世莫知其然否。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0023",
          "zh": "老子，隱君子也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0024",
          "zh": "老子之子名宗，宗為魏將，封於段干。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0025",
          "zh": "宗子注，注子宮，宮玄孫假，假仕於漢孝文帝。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0026",
          "zh": "而假之子解為膠西王卬太傅，因家于齊焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0027",
          "zh": "世之學老子者則絀儒學，儒學亦絀老子。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0028",
          "zh": "「道不同不相為謀」，豈謂是邪？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0029",
          "zh": "李耳無為自化，清靜自正。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0030",
          "zh": "莊子者，蒙人也，名周。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0031",
          "zh": "周嘗為蒙漆園吏，與梁惠王、齊宣王同時。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0032",
          "zh": "其學無所不闚，然其要本歸於老子之言。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0033",
          "zh": "故其著書十餘萬言，大抵率寓言也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0034",
          "zh": "作漁父、盜跖、胠篋，以詆訿孔子之徒，以明老子之術。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0035",
          "zh": "畏累虛、亢桑子之屬，皆空語無事實。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0036",
          "zh": "然善屬書離辭，指事類情，用剽剝儒、墨，雖當世宿學不能自解免也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0037",
          "zh": "其言洸洋自恣以適己，故自王公大人不能器之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0038",
          "zh": "楚威王聞莊周賢，使使厚幣迎之，許以為相。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0039",
          "zh": "莊周笑謂楚使者曰：「千金，重利；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0040",
          "zh": "卿相，尊位也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0041",
          "zh": "子獨不見郊祭之犧牛乎？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0042",
          "zh": "養食之數歲，衣以文繡，以入大廟。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0043",
          "zh": "當是之時，雖欲為孤豚，豈可得乎？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0044",
          "zh": "子亟去，無污我。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0045",
          "zh": "我寧游戲污瀆之中自快，無為有國者所羈，終身不仕，以快吾志焉。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0047",
          "zh": "申不害者，京人也，故鄭之賤臣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0048",
          "zh": "學術以干韓昭侯，昭侯用為相。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0049",
          "zh": "內修政教，外應諸侯，十五年。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0050",
          "zh": "終申子之身，國治兵彊，無侵韓者。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0051",
          "zh": "申子之學本於黃老而主刑名。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0052",
          "zh": "著書二篇，號曰申子。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0053",
          "zh": "韓非者，韓之諸公子也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0054",
          "zh": "喜刑名法術之學，而其歸本於黃老。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0055",
          "zh": "非為人口吃，不能道說，而善著書。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0056",
          "zh": "與李斯俱事荀卿，斯自以為不如非。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0057",
          "zh": "非見韓之削弱，數以書諫韓王，韓王不能用。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0058",
          "zh": "於是韓非疾治國不務修明其法制，執勢以御其臣下，富國彊兵而以求人任賢，反舉浮淫之蠹而加之於功實之上。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0059",
          "zh": "以為儒者用文亂法，而俠者以武犯禁。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0060",
          "zh": "寬則寵名譽之人，急則用介胄之士。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0061",
          "zh": "今者所養非所用，所用非所養。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0062",
          "zh": "悲廉直不容於邪枉之臣，觀往者得失之變，故作孤憤、五蠹、內外儲、說林、說難十餘萬言。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0063",
          "zh": "然韓非知說之難，為說難書甚具，終死於秦，不能自脫。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0064",
          "zh": "說難曰：",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0065",
          "zh": "凡說之難，非吾知之有以說之難也；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0066",
          "zh": "又非吾辯之難能明吾意之難也；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0067",
          "zh": "又非吾敢橫失能盡之難也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0068",
          "zh": "凡說之難，在知所說之心，可以吾說當之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0069",
          "zh": "所說出於為名高者也，而說之以厚利，則見下節而遇卑賤，必棄遠矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0070",
          "zh": "所說出於厚利者也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0071",
          "zh": "而說之以名高，則見無心而遠事情，必不收矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0072",
          "zh": "所說實為厚利而顯為名高者也，而說之以名高，則陽收其身而實疏之；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0073",
          "zh": "若說之以厚利，則陰用其言而顯棄其身。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0074",
          "zh": "此之不可不知也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0075",
          "zh": "夫事以密成，語以泄敗。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0076",
          "zh": "未必其身泄之也，而語及其所匿之事，如是者身危。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0077",
          "zh": "貴人有過端，而說者明言善議以推其惡者，則身危。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0078",
          "zh": "周澤未渥也而語極知，說行而有功則德亡，說不行而有敗則見疑，如是者身危。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0079",
          "zh": "夫貴人得計而欲自以為功，說者與知焉，則身危。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0080",
          "zh": "彼顯有所出事，迺自以為也故，說者與知焉，則身危。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0081",
          "zh": "彊之以其所必不為，止之以其所不能已者，身危。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0082",
          "zh": "故曰：與之論大人，則以為閒己；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0083",
          "zh": "與之論細人，則以為粥權。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0084",
          "zh": "論其所愛，則以為借資；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0085",
          "zh": "論其所憎，則以為嘗己。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0086",
          "zh": "徑省其辭，則不知而屈之；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0087",
          "zh": "汎濫博文，則多而久之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0088",
          "zh": "順事陳意，則曰怯懦而不盡；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0089",
          "zh": "慮事廣肆，則曰草野而倨侮。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0090",
          "zh": "此說之難，不可不知也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0091",
          "zh": "凡說之務，在知飾所說之所敬，而滅其所醜。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0092",
          "zh": "彼自知其計，則毋以其失窮之；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0093",
          "zh": "自勇其斷，則毋以其敵怒之；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0094",
          "zh": "自多其力，則毋以其難概之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0095",
          "zh": "規異事與同計，譽異人與同行者，則以飾之無傷也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0096",
          "zh": "有與同失者，則明飾其無失也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0097",
          "zh": "大忠無所拂悟，辭言無所擊排，迺後申其辯知焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0098",
          "zh": "此所以親近不疑，知盡之難也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0099",
          "zh": "得曠日彌久，而周澤既渥，深計而不疑，交爭而不罪，迺明計利害以致其功，直指是非以飾其身，以此相持，此說之成也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0100",
          "zh": "伊尹為庖，百里奚為虜，皆所由干其上也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0101",
          "zh": "故此二子者，皆聖人也，猶不能無役身而涉世如此其汙也，則非能仕之所設也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0102",
          "zh": "宋有富人，天雨牆壞。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0103",
          "zh": "其子曰「不築且有盜」，其鄰人之父亦云，暮而果大亡其財，其家甚知其子而疑鄰人之父。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0104",
          "zh": "昔者鄭武公欲伐胡，迺以其子妻之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0105",
          "zh": "因問群臣曰： 「吾欲用兵，誰可伐者？」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0106",
          "zh": "關其思曰：「胡可伐。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0107",
          "zh": "迺戮關其思，曰：「胡，兄弟之國也，子言伐之，何也？」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0108",
          "zh": "胡君聞之，以鄭為親己而不備鄭。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0109",
          "zh": "鄭人襲胡，取之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0110",
          "zh": "此二說者，其知皆當矣，然而甚者為戮，薄者見疑。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0111",
          "zh": "非知之難也，處知則難矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0112",
          "zh": "昔者彌子瑕見愛於衛君。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0113",
          "zh": "衛國之法，竊駕君車者罪至刖。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0114",
          "zh": "既而彌子之母病，人聞，往夜告之，彌子矯駕君車而出。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0115",
          "zh": "君聞之而賢之曰：「孝哉，為母之故而犯刖罪！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0116",
          "zh": "與君游果園，彌子食桃而甘，不盡而奉君。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0117",
          "zh": "君曰：「愛我哉，忘其口而念我！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0118",
          "zh": "及彌子色衰而愛弛，得罪於君。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0119",
          "zh": "君曰：「是嘗矯駕吾車，又嘗食我以其餘桃。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0120",
          "zh": "故彌子之行未變於初也，前見賢而後獲罪者，愛憎之至變也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0121",
          "zh": "故有愛於主，則知當而加親；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0122",
          "zh": "見憎於主，則罪當而加疏。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0123",
          "zh": "故諫說之士不可不察愛憎之主而後說之矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0124",
          "zh": "夫龍之為蟲也，可擾狎而騎也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0125",
          "zh": "然其喉下有逆鱗徑尺，人有嬰之，則必殺人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0126",
          "zh": "人主亦有逆鱗，說之者能無嬰人主之逆鱗，則幾矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0127",
          "zh": "人或傳其書至秦。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0128",
          "zh": "秦王見孤憤、五蠹之書，曰：「嗟乎，寡人得見此人與之游，死不恨矣！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0129",
          "zh": "李斯曰：「此韓非之所著書也。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0130",
          "zh": "秦因急攻韓。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0131",
          "zh": "韓王始不用非，及急，乃遣非使秦。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0132",
          "zh": "秦王悅之，未信用。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0133",
          "zh": "李斯、姚賈害之，毀之曰：「韓非，韓之諸公子也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0134",
          "zh": "今王欲并諸侯，非終為韓不為秦，此人之情也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0135",
          "zh": "今王不用，久留而歸之，此自遺患也，不如以過法誅之。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0136",
          "zh": "秦王以為然，下吏治非。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0137",
          "zh": "李斯使人遺非藥，使自殺。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0138",
          "zh": "韓非欲自陳，不得見。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0139",
          "zh": "秦王後悔之，使人赦之，非已死矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0140",
          "zh": "申子、韓子皆著書，傳於後世，學者多有。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0141",
          "zh": "余獨悲韓子為說難而不能自脫耳。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0142",
          "zh": "太史公曰：老子所貴道，虛無，因應變化於無為，故著書辭稱微妙難識。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0143",
          "zh": "莊子散道德，放論，要亦歸之自然。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0144",
          "zh": "申子卑卑，施之於名實。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0145",
          "zh": "韓子引繩墨，切事情，明是非，其極慘礉少恩。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0146",
          "zh": "皆原於道德之意，而老子深遠矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}